review_text: Below expectations. Kulfi and Sweet Lassi were underwhelming. Sweet Lassi was overcooked and dry.
Hands down the best Kulfi I've ever had! Kulfi were all prepared beautifully. Fresh and flavorful!
Worst food ever! Fish Curry  Garlic Naan  Tandoori Roti  and Naan were all wrong. Tandoori Roti made me sick. Never ordering again!
Disaster! Malai Kofta were all stale. Malai Kofta had a weird smell. Completely unacceptable!
